plot: Our Heroes try to cross the Mississippi but are involved in a boating accident and split up again. 10K is drawn into Sketchy and Skeezy's latest scam, resulting in a run in with Escorpion. Playing judge, jury and executioner all in one, Escorpion sentences 10K, Sketchy and Skeezy all to death. Warren and the rest of our Heroes arrive on the scene, but is it too late?

The survivors are crossing the Mississippi in a motor boat and they meet Doc's acquaintances Sketchy and Skeezy. The crooks have just looted Graceland and they advise that there are lots of zombies ahead in the river. Soon they need to jump into the water and 10K accidentally splits from his group and stays with the crooks. Doc insists to wait for 10K while Sketchy and Skeezy plot another scheme. However, they are caught and end with Escorpion that plays the judge to decide whether the trio must die or not. Will it be the end of 10k?—Claudio Carvalho, Rio de Janeiro, Brazil
